data.description: Welcome to this charming 1937 home, tastefully remodeled and upgraded for modern living, nestled in a highly desirable location near downtown Orlando. With its timeless appeal and thoughtful updates, this residence seamlessly combines the allure of a bygone era with the conveniences of today.    This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home welcomes you with its classic architecture and a warm ambiance. As you step inside, you'll discover a carefully curated blend of original features and contemporary enhancements. The living spaces exude a sense of comfort, with the living room providing a cozy retreat, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests.    The kitchen has been thoughtfully redesigned to offer both functionality and style. Modern appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage seamlessly integrate with the home's original character, creating a perfect balance between the old and the new. The adjacent dining area is bathed in natural light, creating a delightful space for family meals or intimate gatherings.    The bedrooms are generously sized, providing comfort and privacy. The master suite is a true sanctuary, offering a tranquil escape with an updated en-suite bathroom. The additional bedrooms are versatile and can be used for guests, a home office, or a creative space.    One of the standout features of this home is its convenient carport, providing shelter for your vehicles and ensuring easy access. The well-manicured yard surrounds the property, offering a peaceful retreat and a perfect spot for outdoor activities.    Situated in a highly sought-after location, this residence is just a stone's throw away from downtown Orlando, offering easy access to a vibrant urban lifestyle with shops, restaurants, and cultural attractions. Moreover, the proximity to all major theme parks adds an extra layer of convenience for entertainment and family fun.    Don't miss the opportunity to own a piece of history while enjoying the comforts of modern living. This meticulously updated home offers a unique blend of character, convenience, and location, making it a truly special place to call home.
